  "title": "PMO Support",
  "description": "<p>Roles\n& Responsibilities:</p><p>·      \nSupport\nPM and PMO to fulfil project execution and delivery</p><p>·      \nDevelop\nand maintain project plans, dashboards, and milestone trackers</p><p>·      \nFacilitate\nproject documentation</p><p>·      \nPerform the administrative tasks related to project\nmanagement tool </p><p>Required\nSkills:</p><p>·      \nBachelor’s\ndegree in business, IT, or related field</p><p>·      \n2+\nyears of experience in project management or PMO roles</p><p>·      \nExperience\nin banking or financial services, preferably in core banking projects</p><p>·      \nFamiliarity\nwith large-scale transformations</p><p>·      \nSolid\nunderstanding of project governance frameworks (e.g., Agile, Waterfall, Hybrid)</p><p>·      \nProficiency\nin tools like MS Project, JIRA, Confluence, Excel, PowerPoint</p><p>Preferred\nQualifications:</p><p>·      \nExperience\nin banking industry transformation program</p><p>·      \nPMP,\nPRINCE2, or similar certification</p><p>·      \nExcellent\ncommunication and documentation skills</p><p>·      \nAnalytical\nmindset with attention to detail</p>",
